#: ../../source/network/domain/rdap.rst:2
msgid "RDAP"
msgstr "RDAP"

#: ../../source/network/domain/rdap.rst:4
msgid ""
"RDAP (Registration Data Access Protocol) 协议是Whois协议的后继，和 Whois "
"协议类似，RDAP协议提供了域名、自治系统、IP地址的信息查询。"
msgstr ""
"RDAP (Registration Data Access Protocol) is the successor to the Whois "
"protocol. Like Whois, RDAP provides lookup capabilities for domain names, "
"autonomous systems, and IP addresses."
